{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuserid:completion:"]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Sets a custom user identifier with completion confirmation.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUserId:completion:"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"setUserId:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"NSString","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"userId"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"completion:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":" (^","kind":"text"},{"text":")(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSError","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"error"},{"kind":"text","text":")) "},{"text":"completion","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The custom user identifier (e.g., database ID, UUID, username)."}]}],"name":"userId"},{"name":"completion","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Block called when the operation completes.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Receives nil on success, or an NSError on failure.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Same as ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"setUserId:"},{"text":" but provides callback when the server operation completes.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Use this when you need to ensure the user ID is set before performing"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"dependent operations like merging user data or tracking critical events."}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Example","text":"Example","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Handle login with guaranteed user ID synchronization:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["class LoginCoordinator {","","    func performLogin(credentials: Credentials,","                      completion: @escaping (Result<User, Error>) -> Void) {","","        APIClient.shared.login(credentials) { result in","            switch result {","            case .success(let user):","                \/\/ Set user ID with confirmation before proceeding","                Pushwoosh.configure.setUserId(user.id) { error in","                    if let error = error {","                        Logger.warning(\"User ID sync failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","                        \/\/ Continue anyway - local state is still valid","                    }","","                    \/\/ Now safe to track login event with correct user attribution","                    Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","                        \"logged_in\": true,","                        \"last_login\": ISO8601DateFormatter().string(from: Date()),","                        \"login_method\": credentials.method.rawValue","                    ])","","                    \/\/ Set email if available","                    if let email = user.email {","                        Pushwoosh.configure.setEmail(email)","                    }","","                    completion(.success(user))","                }","","            case .failure(let error):","                completion(.failure(error))","            }","        }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUserId:completion:"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","title":"setUserId:completion:","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setUserId:completion:","symbolKind":"method","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setUserId:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"role":"symbol"},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setUserId:completion:":{"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUserId:completion:"}],"type":"topic","title":"setUserId:completion:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets a custom user identifier with completion confirmation."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setUserId:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUserId:completion:","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuserid:completion:","role":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[],"role":"symbol","title":"PWConfiguration","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol","title":"PushwooshCore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"type":"topic"}}}